WEBVTT

00:00:01.033 --> 00:00:04.100
(Yuya)
Previously on "Yu‐Gi‐Oh Arc V."

00:00:04.100 --> 00:00:06.766
I send Destiny Hero Dynatag

00:00:06.766 --> 00:00:08.700
from my hand
to the graveyard

00:00:08.700 --> 00:00:10.333
to activate
its special ability!

00:00:10.333 --> 00:00:13.066
(Phoenix)
Since I have fewer
life points than you,

00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:15.100
I don't take damage
from your attack.

00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:17.600
Instead, we both take
1,000 points of damage.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:18.966
(Yuto)
No!

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.366
Aah!

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:30.966
(gasping)

00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:35.633
(tires screeching)

00:00:35.633 --> 00:00:37.100
(man)
This way!

00:00:37.100 --> 00:00:38.200
(man 2)
Commander Phoenix,
are you okay?

00:00:38.200 --> 00:00:39.466
(man)
Do you need help,
Commander Phoenix?

00:00:39.466 --> 00:00:41.466
(thinking)
<i>Commander Phoenix?</i>

00:00:43.333 --> 00:00:46.366
♪♪♪

00:00:52.033 --> 00:00:54.133
♪♪ Hey hey,
Can you feel the power? ♪

00:00:54.133 --> 00:00:56.900
♪♪ You vs. me
Competition for the victory ♪

00:00:56.900 --> 00:00:59.100
♪♪ I could be the best one day
and make history ♪

00:00:59.100 --> 00:01:01.973
♪♪ Swing into action
Are you ready to play? ♪

00:01:01.973 --> 00:01:04.606
♪♪ Challenge anyone anywhere
any day ♪

00:01:04.606 --> 00:01:07.240
♪♪ You wanna take a chance
Go 'head and roll the dice ♪

00:01:07.240 --> 00:01:10.240
♪♪ See if it's in your cards
If you'll pay the price ♪

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:12.973
♪♪ Activate the spell
Let your powers come to life ♪

00:01:12.973 --> 00:01:15.273
♪♪ It's showtime
Who will win the fight? ♪

00:01:15.273 --> 00:01:21.140
♪♪ I'm ready to duel
Go 'head and make your move ♪

00:01:21.140 --> 00:01:24.073
♪♪ I'll win this duel
You can't beat my moves ♪

